widgetTemplates.title: .NET Core
adqlQueryList: SELECT distinctcount(nodeName) AS "Containers" FROM customer_dr_license_v2 WHERE jvmVersion REGEXP "\.NET Core.*" LIMIT 1000

widgetTemplates.title: Nodes por Aplicação
adqlQueryList: SELECT ApplicationName, distinctcount(ifNull(HostName, nodeName)) AS "Nodes" FROM customer_dr_license_v2 WHERE componentTypeName = ".NET Application Server" AND jvmVersion REGEXP "clr.version.*" ORDER BY Nodes desc LIMIT 1000

widgetTemplates.title: Current Search Results
adqlQueryList: SELECT distinctcount(ifNull(HostName, nodeName)) AS "Licenças" FROM customer_dr_license_v2 WHERE componentTypeName  = ".NET Application Server" and jvmVersion REGEXP "clr.*" LIMIT 1500

widgetTemplates.title: Consumo por Aplicação
adqlQueryList: SELECT ApplicationName, distinctcount(nodeId) AS "Licenses" FROM customer_dr_license_v2 WHERE productType = "APP_AGENT" ORDER BY Licenses DESC LIMIT 1000

widgetTemplates.title: Java
adqlQueryList: SELECT distinctcount(nodeId) AS " " FROM customer_dr_license_v2 WHERE productType = "APP_AGENT"

widgetTemplates.title: Node.js
adqlQueryList: SELECT distinctcount(HostName)/10 AS " " FROM customer_dr_license_v2 WHERE productType = "NODEJS_APP_AGENT"

widgetTemplates.title: Python
adqlQueryList: SELECT distinctcount(HostName) AS " " FROM customer_dr_license_v2 WHERE productType = "PYTHON_APP_AGENT"

widgetTemplates.title: Consumo por aplicação
adqlQueryList: SELECT ApplicationName, distinctcount(HostName) AS "Licenses" FROM customer_dr_license_v2 WHERE productType = "NODEJS_APP_AGENT" ORDER BY Licenses desc LIMIT 300

widgetTemplates.title: Consumo por Aplicação
adqlQueryList: SELECT ApplicationName, distinctcount(HostName) AS "Licenses" FROM customer_dr_license_v2 WHERE productType = "PYTHON_APP_AGENT" ORDER BY Licenses DEsc LIMIT 100

widgetTemplates.title: Consumo por Aplicação
adqlQueryList: SELECT ApplicationName, distinctcount(nodeName) AS "Containers" FROM customer_dr_license_v2 WHERE productType = "DOT_NET_APP_AGENT" AND jvmVersion REGEXP "\.NET Core.*" ORDER BY Containers DESC LIMIT 1000

widgetTemplates.title: Current Search Results
adqlQueryList: SELECT distinctcount(application) FROM customer_node_report_v1 WHERE Application NOt like "*HML*"

widgetTemplates.title: Aplicações - PRD
adqlQueryList: SELECT distinctcount(ApplicationName) AS "Total" FROM customer_dr_license_v2 WHERE ApplicationName NOt like "*HML*"

widgetTemplates.title: Aplicações - HML
adqlQueryList: SELECT distinctcount(ApplicationName) AS "Total" FROM customer_dr_license_v2 WHERE ApplicationName like "*HML*"

widgetTemplates.title: Aplicações - UNKNOWN
adqlQueryList: SELECT distinctcount(ApplicationName) AS "Total" FROM customer_dr_license_v2 WHERE ApplicationName NOt like "*HML*" AND ApplicationName NOT like "*PRD*"

widgetTemplates.title: Agent Versions Count - (Reporting)
adqlQueryList: SELECT distinct appAgentVersion, count(nodeName) AS "Agent Version" FROM customer_dr_license_v2 WHERE App_Status > 0 ORDER BY `Agent Version` desc LIMIT 300

widgetTemplates.title: Servidores sem Machine Agent -NOT running NET CORE
adqlQueryList: SELECT distinct HostName, Machine_Agent_Installed FROM customer_dr_license_v2 WHERE Machine_Agent_Installed LIKE "false" AND App_Status > 0 AND jvmVersion not liKE "*NET Core*" LIMIT 1000
